snippet.title: Black Adam - Official Trailer 2
snippet.description:
There are heroes, there are villains and there is #BlackAdam Only in theaters October 21.

THE WORLD NEEDED A HEROâ€¦ IT GOT BLACK ADAM

From New Line Cinema, Dwayne Johnson stars in the action adventure â€œBlack Adam.â€ The first-ever feature film to explore the story of the DC Super Hero comes to the big screen under the direction of Jaume Collet-Serra (â€œJungle Cruiseâ€).

In ancient Kahndaq, Teth Adam was bestowed the almighty powers of the gods. After using these powers for vengeance, he was imprisoned, becoming Black Adam. Nearly 5,000 years have passed and Black Adam has gone from man, to myth, to legend. Now released, his unique form of justice, born out of rage, is challenged by modern day heroes who form the Justice Society: Hawkman, Dr. Fate, Atom Smasher and Cyclone.

Johnson stars alongside Aldis Hodge (â€œCity on a Hill,â€ â€œOne Night in Miamiâ€) as Hawkman, Noah Centineo (â€œTo All the Boys Iâ€™ve Loved Beforeâ€) as Atom Smasher, Sarah Shahi (â€œSex/Life,â€ â€œRush Hour 3â€), Marwan Kenzari (â€œMurder on the Orient Express,â€ â€œThe Mummyâ€), Quintessa Swindell (â€œVoyagers,â€ â€œTrinketsâ€) as Cyclone, Mo Amer (â€œMo,â€ â€œRamyâ€), Bodhi Sabongui (â€œA Million Little Thingsâ€), and Pierce Brosnan (the â€œMamma Mia!â€ and James Bond franchises) as Dr. Fate.

Collet-Serra directed from a screenplay written by Adam Sztykiel and Rory Haines & Sohrab Noshirvani, based on characters from DC, based on characters created by Bill Parker and C.C. Beck. The filmâ€™s producers are Beau Flynn, Hiram Garcia, Dwayne Johnson and Dany Garcia, with Toby Emmerich, Richard Brener, Dave Neustadter, Chris Pan, Walter Hamada, Adam Schlagman, Geoff Johns, Eric McLeod and Scott Sheldon executive producing.

The directorâ€™s behind-the-scenes creative team includes Oscar-nominated director of 
photography Lawrence Sher (â€œJokerâ€), production designer Tom Meyer (â€œReal Steelâ€), editors Mike Sale (â€œRed Notice,â€ â€œSkyscraperâ€) and John Lee (â€œAnyone Home?â€), costume designers Kurt and Bart (â€œDeadpool 2,â€ â€œThe Hunger Games: Mockingjay â€“ Part 1 & 2â€), Oscar-winning visual effects supervisor Bill Westenhofer (â€œLife of Pi,â€ â€œWonder Womanâ€), and composer Lorne Balfe (â€œBlack Widowâ€).

New Line Cinema Presents a Seven Bucks/Flynn Co. Production, A Jaume Collet-Serra Film, â€œBlack Adam,â€ smashing into theaters and IMAX internationally beginning 19 October 2022, in North America on October 21, 2022. It will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.title: Pink Panther Climbs Mount Everest! | 35 Min Compilation | Pink Panther and Pals
snippet.description:
(1) Pink's Peak - Pink Panther and Hoarse are unexpectedly forced to mountain climb. (2) Pink Kahuna - Pink Panther tries to have fun at the beach, but Big Nose makes sure that everyone is not enjoying their time at the beach. (3) Pinkaroni Pizza - After Pink Panther finds his favorite pizza place closed for construction, he is on a mission to make his own pizza. (4) Pink 'n' Putt - Big Nose and Pink Panther go against each other on a mini golf course. (5) Frosted Pink - Pink Panther wants a slushy from Big Nose's store, but Pink Panther keeps making a mess, angering Big Nose, who is a neat freak.

The Pink Panther is the sly, lanky animated cat created by Friz Freleng and David DePatie. The iconic feline was first created in 1964.

AllVideo.video_title: Pink Panther and the Attack of the Clones! | 56 Min Compilation | Pink Panther and Pals

snippet.title: Pink Panther and the Attack of the Clones! | 56 Min Compilation | Pink Panther and Pals
snippet.description:
Pink Panther and the attack of the clones!

(1) Pink Pink Pink Pink - Pink Panther buys a machine that multiplies things. Four Pink Panthers result and the three clones wreak havoc. (2) Noteably Pink - Pink Panther and Big Nose explore different types of music genres and musical instruments. (3) Gold, Silver, Bronze, and Pink - Big Nose, Hoarse, and Pink Panther compete in the Olympic Games. (4) A Fairly Pink Pumpkin - Pink Panther and Big Nose compete in a pumpkin competition. (5) Make Pink Not War - Pink Panther lives between two feuding neighbors and can't seem to find any peace. (6) Wild Pinkdom - Big Nose, a wildlife photographer, is dedicated to finally capture a photo of the elusive Pink Panther. (7) Life in the Pink Lane - Pink Panther and Big Nose compete in a serious game of bowling. (8) Pink Trek - Pink Panther and Big Nose race to deliver a package.

snippet.title: Official Pink Panther
snippet.description:
The Official Pink Panther YouTube Channel. Think Pink!

New episodes of The Pink Panther (1993) will be uploaded every Monday, Thursday, and Saturday!

In 1964, this pink-inked feline slinked onto the opening credits of Blake Edwards' caper film by the same name and threatened to steal the entire show. Sleek, sophisticated and witty, the animation, produced by Friz Freleng and David H. DePatie, was a stylish departure from its contemporaries...and an instant hit. A subsequent short film, The Pink Phink, would go on to win* an OscarÂ® and spawn a celebrated series of six-minute cartoons featuring the sly cat.
